### Get all course files
GET http://localhost:5001/api/files

### Create a new course file
POST http://localhost:5001/api/files
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "course_id": "<uuid>",
  "title": "Lecture 1",
  "file_type": "video",
  "file_url": "/videos/lecture1.mp4",
  "file_order": 1
}

### Get a course file by ID
GET http://localhost:5001/api/files/<uuid>
